{"word":"γαμήλιος","slug":"γαμήλιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>γαμήλιος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:γαμέω'><el>γαμέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>belonging to a wedding, bridal</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>γαμηλία</el> (<a href='S:scilicet'>sc.</a> <el>θυσία</el>), <i>a wedding feast</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}